snippet.title: "They Should Move On" - Elon Musk's Thoughts onJohnny Depp + Amber Heard Lawsuit
snippet.description:
Elon Musk has had quite a few words in regard to the Johnny Depp and Amber Heard lawsuit. Most recently concerning a challenge that consequently led to being challenged by actor Mickey Rourke.

My previous videos on Elon Musk and his drama with Azealia Banks and Grimes:
The short one - https://youtu.be/mqjge2nJsNg
And the long one - https://youtu.be/jlJ-L1J6XB4

Full livestream from this recap available to patreon subscribers: https://www.patreon.com/posts/39837715

0:00 Context to Elon's Challenge To Johnny
1:56 Elon Musk denies affair with Amber Heard and Cara Delevingne
4:50 Why People Think Elon is Lying About Amber Cheating
12:18 The Texts Between "Rocket Man" and Amber
15:49 Johnny Depp's "slicing" reaction

WORKS CITED:
New York Times interview with Elon: https://www.nytimes.com/2020/07/25/style/elon-musk-maureen-dowd.html
Amber's best friend's - Raquel Pennington's - ex husband's deposition: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jzvcQ0OVa6Q
Concierge confirming Elon would visit Johnny's penthouse throughout 2015: https://deadline.com/2020/07/elon-musk-amber-heard-johnny-depps-los-angeles-penthouse-1202988261/
Texts between Elon and Amber revealing her ghosting him: https://usagag.com/amber-heard-ghosted-elon-musk-during-marriage-to-johnny-depp-texts-show/
Mickey Rourke's instagram picture: https://www.instagram.com/p/CDIC7SuHkaA/
Fully sourced website used in the beginning citing information on the case: https://www.ifod.net/thetruth/
